“We will bring the Raid start time forward by two days and immediately unlock the third and fourth bosses, to ensure that Keepers in all time zones can participate in the event as much as possible during its duration.”

Additional clarification: The specific time this change will take effect is tomorrow at 9:00 (UTC+8). Bringing the schedule forward by two days means that tomorrow the 3rd, 4th, and 5th bosses will be opened, with kill counts set at 70K, 80K, and 100K respectively. Please take note and prepare accordingly.

